{"id":"2d8b06fa7732c373f7e55b9fca009d60fb4dd4111df6ad0ba58da2855f35cde3","item_id":"64218d3dd7:0","text":"你可以添加 RenderMan IPR ROP（RenderMan 交互式渲染 ROP），可从"}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"64218d3dd7:1","text":"RenderMan Shelf（RenderMan 工具架）"}
{"id":"39bbf500a316d6e9f6cc3a9e3d262088c077cb40e0255e91b4a92fb2490c9ece","item_id":"64218d3dd7:2","text":"或 /out pane（/out 面板）添加 RenderMan IPR ROP。"}
{"id":"c7da25857d287595bf3d553838fc56e313bd22acae9bd98a5306223dcda1e9aa","item_id":"64218d3dd7:3","text":"使用 RenderMan Shelf（RenderMan 工具架）"}
{"id":"035d810150068e0cce1b2f7cbad8b3b30c17e4f25bb643ee1d6f5ee97cf206fe","item_id":"64218d3dd7:4","text":"我们可以使用 ROP tool（ROP 工具），它位于"}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"64218d3dd7:5","text":"RenderMan Shelf（RenderMan 工具架）"}
{"id":"e42f47e1af122366bccf238fff42184f9ae13b0b8fb44afc3bcd0b5ce9dd91f2","item_id":"64218d3dd7:6","text":"中，用它创建一个 ROP，该 ROP 会自动向你的 RIS Network（RIS 网络）添加 integrator VOP（积分器 VOP）。"}
{"id":"0ff2aae666a6fec465d1d142cdbb0a7b4527111aa78cc18ee10c382472380ca6","item_id":"64218d3dd7:7","text":"使用 out pane（手动配置）"}
{"id":"4090cbb7afacec2fc5197874113eab7a43b75dc4d4c9b905cafc8a2202da019b","item_id":"64218d3dd7:8","text":"添加 RenderMAN IPR ROP（交互式渲染 ROP）"}
{"id":"1062693896582cd8ba2526c5b1d2951822ff9186e67459660d48f85a98a563da","item_id":"64218d3dd7:9","text":"添加 Integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"a09b9fc0e25a43ccbea265f55794b64c0e4e8c5d5eefbca1133c1efea6ba22c7","item_id":"64218d3dd7:10","text":"在你的 RIS Network（RIS 网络）中添加一个 integrator VOP（积分器 VOP），例如"}
{"id":"c66c3367fc146e7ab68fcb67ccdd75c3909cd0bca2343b35b4f46f0cbc0a6a52","item_id":"64218d3dd7:11","text":"PxrPathTracer"}
{"id":"bebccb340f3196f7687c289303f4d2c531967972aebb252fa232f96111a88fb1","item_id":"64218d3dd7:12","text":"设置 Integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"775f5de953bcdb7576d990969982f8530ad1738dfe9d7ea66b0c379ab7e0e076","item_id":"64218d3dd7:13","text":"只需将你的 integrator VOP（积分器 VOP）路径拖到"}
{"id":"e43f447b65e6b1236fa237ffc613d5e0dde3509a5d3089e6378686e41318d17a","item_id":"64218d3dd7:14","text":"Integrator（积分器）"}
{"id":"b36ef3235e1311f00561825c1504a68042e9d20ff872a7d686413a61b9faf698","item_id":"64218d3dd7:15","text":"中，该参数位于 RenderMan RIS ROP 内。如果跳过此步骤，默认会使用 PxrPathTracer integrator（PxrPathTracer 积分器）及其默认参数。"}
